\v 21 Therefore \em God\em* with an oath gave to him glory in his folk; \em God made\em* him to increase, as an heap of earth, and to enhance his seed as \sls (the)\sls* stars, and to inherit them from the sea unto the sea, from the flood \sls (or the river)\sls* unto the ends of \sls (the)\sls* earth. 
