\p  
\v 1 And he kept to him men of mercy, finding grace in the sight of each man \add [or of all flesh]\add*. Moses was loved of \sls (or by)\sls* God and of \sls (or by)\sls* men; whose mind \sls (or memory)\sls* is in blessing. 
