\p  
\v 1 Jesus \sls (or Joshua the son of)\sls* Nun, the successor of Moses in prophets \sls (or in prophecies)\sls*, \em was\em* strong in battle, that was great by \add [or after]\add* his name. The greatest into the health \sls (or the deliverance)\sls* of \sls (the)\sls* chosen men of God, to overcome enemies rising against \em them\em*, \sls (so)\sls* that he should get the heritage of Israel. 
