\v 11 Christ\f + \fr 47:11 \ft All modern translations have “The Lord” here.\f* purged the sins of him, and enhanced his horn without end; and he gave to him the testament of kings, and the seat \add [or a seat]\add* of glory in Israel. 
\p  
