\p  
\v 4 So Elijah was alarged, \sls (or en-larged, or magnified)\sls* in his marvels; and who may have glory in like manner with thee, 
\p  
\v 5 which tookest away a dead man from hells, \add [or hell]\add*, \sls (or from the grave)\sls*, \sls (yea)\sls*, from the heritage of death, in the word of the Lord God?\sls (.)\sls* 
\p  
